{"id":"upfunda","label":"UpFunda Level 1","list":[{"label":"1. Doubles Addition","id":"doubles","type":"completePuzzle","data":{"type":"rightOpen","title":"Drag and drop the correct block that make the addition right.","fontSize":"2rem","text":"1 + 1,  = 2, = 3\n         2 + 2, = 4, = 2\n         3 + 3, = 6, = 8\n         4 + 4, = 8, = 10\n         5 + 5, = 10, = 12\n         6 + 6, = 12, = 11\n         7 + 7, = 14, = 13\n         8 + 8, = 16, = 18\n         9 + 9, = 18, = 14,\n         10 + 10, = 20,  = 18"}},{"type":"dominos","id":"dominos","label":"2. Count Dominos","data":{"type":2}},{"type":"group","id":"family-10-15","label":"3. 10 & 15 Family","data":{"title":"Group the below items as 10 family or 15 family.","types":[{"name":"Family of 10","text":"3 + 7 = 10, 7 + 3 = 10, 10 − 3 = 7, 10 − 7 = 3"},{"name":"Family of 15","text":"8 + 7 = 15, 7 + 8 = 15, 15 − 7 = 8, 15 − 8 = 7"}]}},{"type":"group","id":"family-11-7","label":"3. 11 & 7 Family","data":{"title":"Group the below items as 11 family or 7 family.","fontSize":"2rem","types":[{"name":"Family of 11","text":"6 + 5 = 11, 5 + 6 = 11, 11 − 5 = 6, 11 − 6 = 5"},{"name":"Family of 7","text":"4 + 3 = 7, 3 + 4 = 7, 7 − 3 = 4, 7 − 4 = 3"}]}},{"type":"memoryFindPair","id":"find-pair","label":"4. Find Shape Pairs","onlyBigScreen":true,"data":{"canvasWidth":800,"size":140,"imgType":"svg","imgs":[[{"d":"M 10 30 H 130 V 110 H 10 Z","fill":"#ff3838","info":"rect"}],[{"d":"M 10 70 a 60 60 0 1 0 120 0 a 60 60 0 1 0 -120 0","fill":"#17659e","info":"circle"}],[{"d":"M 10 10 H 130 V 130 H 10 Z","fill":"#2fd3d3","info":"square"}],[{"d":"M 70 10 L 130 130 H 10 Z","fill":"#ff3838","info":"triangle"}],[{"d":"M 70 10L 127 51L 105 119L 35 119L 13 51 Z","fill":"#ff7100","info":"pentagon"}],[{"d":"M 70 10L 122 40L 122 100L 70 130L 18 100L 18 40 Z","fill":"#ff748c","info":"hexagon"}]]}},{"type":"fourColor","id":"fourColor","label":"5. Four Shapes Game","data":{"color":"#08b8ff","type":"shapes","title":"Rearrange the shapes and align the same types together.","paths":["v 40 h 40 v -40 0 z","m 0 20 a 20 20 0 1 0 40 0 a 20 20 0 1 0 -40 0","m 20 0 l 20 40 h -40 z","m 20 0 l 19 14 l -7 24 l -24 0 l -7 -22 z"],"text":"133\n021\n012\n023"}},{"label":"6. Count Arithmetic","type":"countArithmetic","id":"count-arithmetic","data":{"type":"addition","title":"Add 10: Count the fruits and add them","arr":[[1,9],[2,8],[3,7],[4,6],[5,5]]}},{"type":"quickArithmetic","id":"addition","label":"7. Add single digit number to 2 digit number","data":{"type":"add~xx~x"}},{"label":"8. Add the numbers in the Abacus","type":"placeValueAbacus","id":"abacus-add","onlyBigScreen":true,"data":{"pattern":"xxx","list":[345,234,235,699,696],"type":"construct","title":"Add the numbers in the Abacus","problems":[["222","+","123"],["113","+","121"],["35","+","200"],["382","+","317"],["592","+","104"]]}},{"type":"quickArithmetic","id":"subtraction","label":"9. Subtract single digit number to 2 digit number","data":{"type":"sub~xx~x"}},{"label":"10. Find the Problem in Numberline","type":"numberLine","id":"number-line-2","lockAfter":1,"data":{"title":"What problem the below numberline represents?","type":"read","range":110,"minorLines":5,"labelGap":5,"unit":100,"text":"20-5\n        16+4\n        18-4\n        10+7\n        100-10"}},{"label":"11. Working Backwards – Fill up by dragging","type":"matchByDragDrop","id":"match-backward","data":{"title":"Drag and Drop the numbers at the right places.","dashWidth":60,"fontSize":"2rem","dashHeight":"3rem","text":"*12* + 2 = 14 \n*13* − 3 = 10 \n*14* + 6 = 20 \n*20* − 5 = 15  \n*4* + 9 = 13 "}},{"label":"12. Subtract the numbers in the Abacus","type":"placeValueAbacus","id":"abacus-subtract","onlyBigScreen":true,"data":{"pattern":"xxx","list":[130,613,401,112,152],"type":"construct","title":"Subtract the numbers in the Abacus","problems":[["542","−","412"],["795","−","182"],["832","−","431"],["292","−","180"],["653","−","501"]]}},{"id":"evaluate","type":"quickArithmetic","label":"13. Mental calculation made easy","lockAfter":2,"data":{"title":"Evaluate","allowNegative":true,"text":"54+10\n        76-10\n        19-10\n        43+10\n        99-10\n        12+10\n        43+100\n        201-100\n        433-100\n        549+100"}},{"id":"match","label":"10. Match the Equals","type":"match","data":{"canvasWidth":"600px","title":"Match the Equals","text":"5 less than 20 , 20 − 5\n        5 more than 20, 20 + 5\n        5 less than 15, 15 − 5\n        5 more than 15, 15 + 5\n        5 more than 25, 25 + 5\n        5 less than 25, 25 − 5"}},{"type":"balance","label":"14. Balance Scale Addition","id":"balance","data":{"fontSize":"1.5rem","arr":["3, 0\n?, 3\n0, 1, 2, 3","1,4\n ?, 3\n2, 1, 3, 0","7,4\n?, 5\n6, 7, 5, 4","2, 5\n?, 5\n2, 3, 1, 0","6, 12\n?, 8\n10, 11, 9, 12"]}},{"type":"mathCrossword","label":"15. Subtraction: Fill the boxes","id":"mathcross","data":{"title":"Click on the empty cells and fill it with the correct number.","text":"12−7=?\n−b−b−\n5−3=?\n=b=b=\n?−?=?","answer":[5,2,7,4,3]}},{"type":"balance","label":"16. Missing Number in Addition","id":"balance-2","data":{"fontSize":"1.5rem","arr":["2, ?\n1, 16\n15, 5, 16, 14","?, 3\n1, 9\n7, 8, 5, 6","?, 12\n3, 9\n0, 1, 2,3","8, 0\n0, ?\n8, 4, 3, 6","0, 2\n1, ?\n1, 2, 3, 0"]}},{"type":"mathCrossword","label":"17. Missing Number in Subtraction","id":"mathcross-2","data":{"title":"Click on the empty cells and fill it with the correct number.","text":"12−?=6\n−b−b−\n?−?=?\n=b=b=\n5−?=1","answer":[6,7,2,5,4]}},{"label":"19. Say No to Fingers","type":"sorting","id":"sort-no-finger","data":{"title":"Sort the learning","text":"Doubles Addition\n        Doubles + 1\n        Doubles + 2\n        Magic 10 upto 10\n        Magic 10 upto 100\n        Using 1-100 chart, Adding +10\n        Using 1-100 chart, Adding +20\n        Using 1-100 chart, Adding +30\n        Using 1-100 chart, two digit number addition "}},{"type":"quickArithmetic","id":"after-number","label":"20. After Number","data":{"type":"after~xx"}}